# RELOAD CONFIGURATION (zero-downtime):
#   docker exec caddy caddy reload
#
# VIEW ACTIVE ROUTES:
#   docker exec caddy caddy routes
#
# LIST CERTIFICATES:
#   docker exec caddy caddy list-certs
#
# CHECK SYNTAX:
#   caddy validate --config Caddyfile
#
# TROUBLESHOOTING:
#   - Certificate not issuing: Check docker logs caddy (ACME errors)
#   - Proxy errors 502: Verify backend service is running
#   - Timeout issues: Check Tailscale connectivity (ping 10.10.10.50 from VPS)
#   - HTTPS upgrade loop: Clear browser cache or use incognito mode
#
